# Project Conventions

**Follow existing project conventions exactly.** Before writing new code, read nearby files that solve a similar problem and mirror how they do it.

Stack: **React 19**, **TypeScript** (strict), **TanStack Start/Router**, **TanStack React Query**, **Tailwind CSS v4**, **shadcn/ui** (Radix), **lucide-react**, **uPlot** for charts.

## Layout

| Area | Location |
|------|----------|
| Routes | `src/routes/` ‚Äî TanStack file-based routing (`routeTree.gen.ts` is generated) |
| UI primitives | `src/components/ui/` ‚Äî shadcn components |
| App components | `src/components/` |
| API client | `src/lib/api/client.ts` + domain modules (`servers.ts`, `admin/`, etc.) |
| Query options | `src/lib/api/*.queries.ts` ‚Äî React Query `queryOptions` factories |
| Auth | `src/lib/auth/` ‚Äî context, session helpers, validation |
| Metrics / charts | `src/lib/metrics/` ‚Äî range, series, chart config, uPlot theme |
| Utilities | `src/lib/` |
| Hooks | `src/hooks/` |
| Global styles / theme | `src/styles.css` |
| Path alias | `@/*` ‚Üí `src/*` |

## Integration points

- **New pages** ‚Äî add a route file under `src/routes/`; wire into `SiteHeader` nav if needed.
- **API calls** ‚Äî use `apiFetch` from `@/lib/api/client`; default `credentials: "include"` for cookie auth. Use `queryOptions` + `useQuery`/`useMutation` ‚Äî don't scatter raw `fetch`.
- **Metrics charts** ‚Äî use existing chart helpers (`build-chart-config`, `metric-timeseries`, `uplot-theme`); align time windows with `MetricTimeRange` / `MetricTimeWindow`.
- **UI primitives** ‚Äî match existing `src/components/ui/` patterns (CVA variants, `cn()`, Radix primitives, `Slot`).
- **Styling** ‚Äî Tailwind utilities merged with `cn()` from `@/lib/utils`. Use theme tokens from `styles.css` (`bg-monitor-gray-100`, `text-warning`, `text-success`, `text-error`, shadcn semantic tokens) ‚Äî not raw `neutral-*` scales or one-off hex. See `design-system.mdc`.
- **Inline `style`** ‚Äî avoid for colors, spacing, and typography that belong in Tailwind or theme tokens. Use `style` only when the value is computed at runtime: chart dimensions, tooltip positioning.
- **Icons** ‚Äî `lucide-react`, consistent sizing with sibling components.
- **Destructive actions** ‚Äî confirm in a `Dialog` with plain-English summary; toast on successful save (`sonner`).
- **Secrets** ‚Äî never store passwords or session secrets in client code. Auth is cookie-based only.

## Component design

**Model variation with types, not branching.** Use discriminated unions, CVA variant props, composition, or separate components ‚Äî not string flags with `switch` chains.

- **Server status / metrics** ‚Äî dedicated chart cards and dashboard components under `src/components/dashboard/` and `src/components/metrics/`.
- **Shared logic belongs up the tree** ‚Äî extract a hook or shared component when multiple call sites need it.
- **Only where it earns its keep** ‚Äî one variant with no second implementation stays concrete.

## Surrounding context

**Read the subsystem before you write code.**

- Trace an existing page end-to-end (route ‚Üí components ‚Üí query options ‚Üí API client) before adding a sibling.
- Check `__root.tsx` / `SiteHeader` for layout and nav before changing page structure.
- No loose workarounds ‚Äî don't bypass `apiFetch`, shadcn patterns, or the `@/` alias with one-off hacks.
